<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to Octa!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Octa, {{adminName}}!</h2>
        <p>Your organization <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong> has been successfully onboarded.</p>
        <p>To activate your administrator account, please verify your email address:</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{verifyLink}}" class="button">
                Verify Email Address
            </a>
        </p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <footer>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Octa Team</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>